message.entry: Input Path must contain a minimum of 3 path points for optimization.
First argument must be an N-by-2 or N-by-3 matrix, or navPath object with SE(2) state space.
{0} argument must be of type binaryOccupancyMap, occupancyMap, or Name for a valid Name-Value pair.
The current robot state {0} is not obstacle-free. Check the start state or update map.
The last state {0} of the ReferencePath is not obstacle-free. Update the ReferencePath or Map.
The input path must contain at least one pose in which the travel direction is non-orthogonal to the orientation vector.
The structure assigned to {0} does not contain fields {1}.
Input Path must have minimum 2 path points to compute the heading.
LookAheadTime must be at least {0} seconds. LookAheadTime must be at least three times greater than ReferenceDeltaTime for controllerMPPI to find a path.
The dimensions of VehicleInputsStandardDeviation must match dimensions of VehicleModel Inputs.
